title: United Kingdom Imports of Pharmaceutical Products
description: Imports of Pharmaceutical Products in the United Kingdom decreased to 2206.69 GBP Million in September from 2328.84 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Pharmaceutical Products in the United Kingdom averaged 1259.47 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 3164.66 GBP Million in March of 2019 and a record low of 300.79 GBP Million in April of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Pharmaceutical Products.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
